data.description: Motivated Seller. The entire house has been freshly painted, light and bright. New hardware installed. Solar is installed and transferrable to qualified buyers, $99/mo. which keeps your PNM bill at $8 month.  Master Cool and newer windows in the dining room and living room. There is a heated extra room with attached workshop, this area has endless possibilities, movie room, music room, 4th bedroom, art studio, den.  The large backyard has a large extended patio the width of the house and beautiful, raised planter beds and mountain views.  Storage shed conveys. Newer roof and Master Cool in 2017 Newer Refrigerator and Dishwasher in 2018. No carpet, tile throughout and brink entry. Convenient located close to the base, VA, dining and shopping.  This property has so much potential
